cuems-videocomposer (0.1.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Implement async video loading to prevent playback interruption
    - Video files are now loaded in a background thread
    - Main render loop continues smoothly during file loading
    - Eliminates momentary playback stutter when loading new videos into layers
    - Clean unused variabes

 -- Ion Reguera <ion@stagelab.coop>  Fri, 12 Dec 2025 18:32:17 +0100

cuems-videocomposer (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian package release
  * NDI input support with bundled NDI SDK libraries
  * Hardware-accelerated video decoding (VAAPI, CUDA, QSV)
  * Multi-layer video composition
  * MTC timecode synchronization
  * HAP codec support
  * OSC remote control support
  * Wayland and X11 display backends
  * DRM/KMS direct rendering support
  * Based on xjadeo codebase

 -- Ion Reguera <ion@stagelab.coop>  Wed, 10 Dec 2025 18:45:42 +0100

